stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PENDING: User selects seat

    PENDING --> CONFIRMED: Payment successful
    PENDING --> CANCELLED: User cancels / Timeout

    CONFIRMED --> CANCELLED: User requests cancellation
    CONFIRMED --> COMPLETED: Show time passed

    CANCELLED --> [*]
    COMPLETED --> [*]

    note right of PENDING: Seat is temporarily held for 10 minutes
    note right of CONFIRMED: Seat is permanently assigned to user
    note right of CANCELLED: Seat becomes available again
    note right of COMPLETED: Movie has been watched
